    {
      "instruction": "<p>Divide the mixture into 4 <span class=\"text-danger\">[8]</span> and shape into patties – these are your <strong>chickpea kofte patties</strong></p><p>Line a baking tray with <strong>baking paper</strong>, drizzle with 1 tsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong> and add the <strong>chickpea kofte patties</strong></p><p>Sprinkle over <strong>half</strong> of the <strong>nigella seeds</strong> (save the rest for later!) and press them gently into the patties</p><p>Put the tray in the oven for 20-25 min or until golden</p>",
      "order": 3,
