    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, cut the <strong>sweet potatoes</strong> (skins on) into fries</p><p>Add the<strong> sweet potato</strong> <strong>fries</strong> to a large baking tray with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Put the tray in the oven for 20 min or until the fries are tender and starting to crisp</p>",
