    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the fries are cooking, finely dice <strong>half</strong> the <strong>cucumber</strong> then grate the <strong>remaining cucumber</strong></p><p>Squeeze the water out of the <strong>grated cucumber</strong> then add to a bowl along with the <strong>natural yoghurt </strong>and <strong>mint sauce</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>raita</strong></p>",
