      "instruction": "<p>Wash the<strong> baby leaf salad</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Add the <strong>diced cucumber</strong> to a bowl along with the <strong>baby leaf salad</strong>, juice of 1 <span class=\"text-danger\">[2]</span> <strong>lemon wedge</strong> and the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>nigella seeds </strong>– this is your <strong>cucumber salad</strong></p>",
